{"type":"message","id":"a57f0d67","parentId":"777cda53","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:22:37.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了！从日志中可以看到 coding agent 频繁出现 \"Path escapes workspace root\" 错误，这说明 coding agent 试图写入超出其工作空间根目录的路径，导致操作失败。\n\n具体问题包括：\n1. **路径越界问题**：coding agent 试图写入 `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace` 但被拒绝，因为路径超出了工作空间根目录\n2. **文件不存在**：多次尝试编辑 `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace/openclaw/src/web/media.ts` 但文件不存在\n3. **工作空间配置问题**：agent 的工作空间路径配置可能不正确\n\n让我检查一下 coding agent 的配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3aeb47ebd1f6455a91bc0a06","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/AGENT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":17600,"output":188,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17788,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772418149698}}
