{"type":"message","id":"9b3d46fc","parentId":"85c0bfec","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:22:40.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我检查主工作空间中的 AGENT 配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46c3cebeb0574d4db034c9a9","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":17817,"output":45,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17862,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772418157111}}
{"type":"message","id":"58609365","parentId":"9b3d46fc","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:22:40.992Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_46c3cebeb0574d4db034c9a9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AGENTS.md - Workspace Guide\n\n## Session Checklist\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday)\n4. **Main session only**: Read `MEMORY.md`\n\n## Memory Files\n- **Daily**: `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` — raw logs\n- **Long-term**: `MEMORY.md` — curated wisdom\n\nWrite important things down. Mental notes die on restart.\n\n## Safety\n- Don't share private data\n- Ask before destructive commands (`trash` > `rm`)\n\n## Group Chat Rules\n- **Speak when**: Directly asked, can add value, correcting misinfo\n- **Stay silent**: Casual banter, already answered, would interrupt vibe\n- **Reactions**: Use emoji (👍 ❤️ 😂 🤔) to acknowledge without cluttering\n\n## Heartbeats\nRead `HEARTBEAT.md`, follow checklist if needed. Reply `HEARTBEAT_OK` if nothing to report.\n\n## Tools\nCheck skill's `SKILL.md`. Local notes go in `TOOLS.md`.\n\n**Formatting:**\n- Discord/WhatsApp: No tables, use bullets\n- Discord links: `<https://example.com>` to suppress embeds\n- WhatsApp: No headers, use **bold** instead\n\n---\n_Make it yours. Update as you learn._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772418160988}}
