{"type":"message","id":"c349f205","parentId":"21675a36","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:45:27.776Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dcd42776a40e430f81e0ee08","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"openclaw sessions_spawn tool documentation\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 984,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"076fed8f1900830a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Tools - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"076fed8f1900830a\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"71b7805a988c22b6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhen running in a sandboxed agent session, session tools default to spawned-only visibility (see below). Row shape (JSON): ... Fetch transcript for one session. Parameters: sessionKey (required; accepts session key or sessionId from sessions_list) ... Returns messages array in the raw transcript format. When given a sessionId, OpenClaw resolves it to the corresponding session key (missing ids error).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"71b7805a988c22b6\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3243585a4137a7bb\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEnhancement: Spawn Verification & Worker Health Monitoring · Issue #8995 · openclaw/openclaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3243585a4137a7bb\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/8995\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8fc77e3f7383cab8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDocumentation: Update AGENTS.md and SKILLS.md with best practices · Until this proposal is implemented, coordinators can approximate verification: #!/bin/bash # spawn_and_verify.sh - Client-side workaround SESSION=$(<strong>openclaw sessions spawn</strong> --task ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8fc77e3f7383cab8\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"4 weeks ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ebcc1255abd49fb7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw Setup Guide: 25 Tools + 53 Skills Explained | WenHao Yu\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ebcc1255abd49fb7\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://yu-wenhao.com/en/blog/openclaw-tools-skills-tutorial/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8a9c4926110b5981\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nsessions_list and sessions_history view sessions. session_status checks status. sessions_send and sessions_spawn <strong>enable inter-session communication and spawning sub-tasks</strong>. Lets OpenClaw send messages to Discord, Slack, Telegram, WhatsApp, iMessage.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8a9c4926110b5981\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"4 weeks ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"yu-wenhao.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ac4a9aca294d8669\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Tools – OpenClaw - Open Source AI Assistant\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ac4a9aca294d8669\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclawcn.com/en/docs/concepts/session-tool/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b26852073143b1b3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSub-agents default to the full tool set minus session tools (configurable via tools.subagents.tools). Sub-agents are not allowed to call sessions_spawn (no sub-agent → sub-agent spawning). Always non-blocking: returns { status: &quot;accepted&quot;, runId, childSessionKey } immediately. After completion, OpenClaw runs a sub-agent announce step and posts the result to the requester chat channel.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b26852073143b1b3\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"1 week ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclawcn.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cbea012a59d82258\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTools (OpenClaw) - OpenClaw Docs | Learn OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cbea012a59d82258\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.learnclawdbot.org/docs/tools\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2880a76ee9f84895\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nList agent ids that the current session may target with sessions_spawn.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2880a76ee9f84895\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.learnclawdbot.org\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"openclaw sessions_spawn tool documentation","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":984,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"076fed8f1900830a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSession Tools - OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"076fed8f1900830a\">>>","url":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"71b7805a988c22b6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhen running in a sandboxed agent session, session tools default to spawned-only visibility (see below). Row shape (JSON): ... Fetch transcript for one session. Parameters: sessionKey (required; accepts session key or sessionId from sessions_list) ... Returns messages array in the raw transcript format. When given a sessionId, OpenClaw resolves it to the corresponding session key (missing ids error).\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"71b7805a988c22b6\">>>","siteName":"docs.openclaw.ai"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3243585a4137a7bb\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEnhancement: Spawn Veri