{"type":"message","id":"139b78c9","parentId":"ddd6d080","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:46:43.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在让我检查 coding agent 是否可以被配置为允许使用 sessions_spawn。根据文档，需要在 coding agent 的配置中添加 `subagents.allowAgents`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"coding\",\n  \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace\",\n  \"subagents\": {\n    \"allowAgents\": [\"*\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n但是，即使这样配置了，**coding agent 本身并不是通过 sessions_spawn 创建的 sub-agent**，它是独立的 agent，所以它本来就应该有完整的工具权限。\n\n让我检查一下 coding agent 实际上是否有 sessions_spawn 权限。让我查看 coding agent 的实际运行情况：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1a867d8f71514bf7a3b0439c","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"kinds":["other"]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":48026,"output":164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772419595037}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad358399","parentId":"139b78c9","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:46:43.602Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1a867d8f71514bf7a3b0439c","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 1,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1772419503198,\n      \"sessionId\": \"ed911667-53fe-4a15-a1b9-cd9734fa790a\",\n      \"model\": \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 262144,\n      \"totalTokens\": 29298,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/ed911667-53fe-4a15-a1b9-cd9734fa790a.jsonl\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":1,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1772419503198,"sessionId":"ed911667-53fe-4a15-a1b9-cd9734fa790a","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","contextTokens":262144,"totalTokens":29298,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/ed911667-53fe-4a15-a1b9-cd9734fa790a.jsonl"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772419603599}}
