{"type":"message","id":"154082da","parentId":"3c9117d9","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:50:05.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到配置中已经启用了 `agentToAgent: { enabled: true }`，但是会话工具的可见性可能被限制了。让我检查一下是否有 `tools.sessions.visibility` 配置：\n\n在配置中我没有看到 `tools.sessions.visibility` 设置，这意味着它使用默认值 `\"tree\"`（当前会话 + spawned subagent sessions）。\n\n由于 coding agent 是一个独立的 agent（不是由 main agent spawn 的 sub-agent），所以 main agent 无法直接通过 `sessions_send` 与它通信。\n\n让我尝试另一种方式 - 通过 Telegram group 来协调。根据配置，你们都在同一个 Telegram group `-1003661163902` 中。\n\n让我先确认 coding agent 的状态：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2e6982270de04248a97a12e4","name":"message","arguments":{"channel":"telegram","target":"-1003661163902","message":"@one_coding_bot Hi, this is the main agent. I'd like to discuss the session_spawn issue with you. Are you available for a quick chat about how to handle your long-running task interruptions?"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":51774,"output":246,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52020,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772419791602}}
